        <div class="card-headline"><h4 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/news/public-health/vital-state-farmers-market-program-on-the-chopping-block/article_9def834a-de11-427b-bdb2-a4bd7e266e01.html" class="tnt-asset-link" aria-label="‘Vital’ farmers-market program on the chopping block — again">
        

        
            ‘Vital’ farmers-market program on the chopping block — again</a></h4></div>
    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">Market Match, a statewide CalFresh program that matches dollars spent at farmers markets up to $15 per visit, is at risk</p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    <article class="clearfix card author  card-author-2cb79574-e84e-11ed-9597-3fcfd009da36">
                <div class="card-container">
                    <div class="media-list">
